; Test has_cost, cost, price posting expressions (exercises post.cc get_has_cost/get_cost/get_price)

2024/01/15 * Buy Stock
    Assets:Brokerage       10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/20 * Buy More
    Assets:Brokerage       5 AAPL @ $155.00
    Assets:Checking

test reg --format "%(has_cost ? \"COST:\" : \"NOCOST:\") %(amount) %(cost) %(price)\n" -> 0
COST: 10 AAPL {$150} [2024/01/15] $1500 $1500
NOCOST: $-1500 $-1500 $-1500
COST: 5 AAPL {$155} [2024/01/20] $775 $775
NOCOST: $-775 $-775 $-775
end test
